&lt;h1 id="knowledge-makes-the-existence-of-resources-infinite"&gt;Knowledge Makes the Existence of Resources Infinite&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dec 10 2021&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&amp;rsquo;re going to keep creating new knowledge and new resources&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Brett:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge is the thing that makes the existence of resources infinite. The creation of knowledge is unbounded. We&amp;rsquo;re going to keep on creating more knowledge and, thereby, learning about more and different resources.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Pessimism Seems Like an Intellectually Serious Position</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/pessimism-seems-like-an-intellectually-serious-position/</link><pubDate>Mon, 17 May 2021 19:49:42 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/pessimism-seems-like-an-intellectually-serious-position/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/pessimism-seems-like-an-intellectually-serious-position.zh/"&gt;中文版本&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
